cannonGame.bullets

Class BulletsCartridge

  • java.lang.Object
    • cannonGame.bullets.BulletsCartridge

  • public class BulletsCartridge
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates and holds separate lists of different types of ammo objects. Game uses these fixed quantity of ammo objects to avoid creating excessive objects.
